        "category": "summary",
        "text": "By sending a specially crafted DHCP response to a client\u2019s DHCP request, an unprivileged remote attacker could execute arbitrary code.",
        "title": "Risk evaluation"
      },
      {
        "category": "other",
        "text": "CRITICAL INFRASTRUCTURE SECTORS: Chemical, Energy, Food and Agriculture, Healthcare and Public Health, Transportation Systems, and Water and Wastewater Systems",
